org.apache.gora

Annotation Type GoraVersionAnnotation


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=PACKAGE)
public @interface GoraVersionAnnotation
    A package attribute that captures the version of Gora that was compiled. This implementation reflects that used in Apache Hadoop.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      String date
      Get the date when Gora was compiled.
      String revision
      Get the subversion revision.
      String srcChecksum
      Get a checksum of the source files from which Gora was compiled.
      String url
      Get the url for the subversion repository.
      String user
      Get the username .
      String version
      Get the Gora version
